# {{SELLER_NAME}}

A [ChainLens](https://github.com/lejuho/ChainLens) seller for
`{{TASK_TYPE}}`.

## Develop

```bash
pnpm install
pnpm dev                 # http://localhost:{{PORT}}
curl http://localhost:{{PORT}}/health
```

## Implement

Edit `src/handler.ts` and return a JSON object matching the
`{{TASK_TYPE}}` schema. Schema lives in `@chainlens/shared/task-types`.

## Deploy

```bash
npx @chainlens/create-seller deploy
```

This wraps `vercel --prod`. Requires `vercel login` once.

## Register

After deploy succeeds, register the URL with the gateway:

```bash
npx @chainlens/create-seller register \
  --task-type {{TASK_TYPE}} \
  --price 0.05 \
  --wallet 0xYourPayoutAddress
```
